title: Zeit Wine Vinegar 9/23: Breonna Taylor, Rittenhouse, Palmetto Cheese, Rolling Stone
itunes:title: Zeit Wine Vinegar 9/23: Breonna Taylor, Rittenhouse, Palmetto Cheese, Rolling Stone
description:
On this edition of Zeit Wine Vinegar Jack and Miles discuss the results of the Breonna Taylor trial, 4 people have filed a civil rights lawsuit against Kyle Rittenhouse and Facebook, the owner of Palmetto Cheese, Brian Henry, called BLM "terrorists", and Rolling Stone released a "500 Best Albums of All Time" list.
